#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kwalletmanager; serves a number of functions. Firstly it allows you to "
#| "see if any wallets are open, which wallets those are, and which "
#| "applications are using each wallet. You can disconnect an application's "
#| "access to a wallet from within the &kwalletmanager;."
msgid ""
