msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as the screen saver starts. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Luk tegnebogen så snart pauseskærmen startes. Når en tegnebog lukkes, "
"behøves kodeord for at få adgang til den igen."

